Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/db_host
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Database host:
 Which database host should be used for this drupal site?
 You can leave this blank to connect via UNIX sockets

Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/db_port
Type: string
Default:
Description: Database port:
 Which database port should be used for this drupal site?
 You can leave this blank for the default

Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/db_user
Type: string
Default: peoplestimes-pilot
Description: Database username:
 Which username should be used to connect to the database?

Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/db_pass
Type: string
Default:
Description: Database password:
 Which password should be used to connect to the database? - leave blank for none

Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/db_database
Type: string
Default: peoplestimes-pilot-drupal
Description: Database name
 Which database should be connected to?

Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/servername
Type: string
Default:
Description: Server name:
 This is the servername of the peoplestimes-pilot drupal install.
 .
 Note that this is just the domain name, so for "http://my.site.com" you only
 need to enter "my.site.com"

Template: drupal-site-peoplestimes-pilot/serverredirects
Type: string
Default:
Description: Server redirects:
 Comma separated list of domain names that the server should permanently
 redirect to the server name.
 .
 Note that this is just the domain name, so for "http://my.site.com" you only
 need to enter "my.site.com"
